  <chunk id="b0321c49afd322bf426b0dfb3eca1152a69ed168.c6" text="In this study, we aimed to determine the effects of endogenous apelin on Ang II-induced pathology in the heart. We showed that Ang II-mediated cardiac dysfunction, hypertrophy, and fibrosis were augmented in apelin knockout (Apelin KO) mice."/>
